### Test E-Commerce API Endpoints

### Get all customers
GET http://localhost:5014/api/customers

### Get customer by ID
GET http://localhost:5014/api/customers/1

### Create a new customer
POST http://localhost:5014/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "surname": "Williams",
  "email": "alice.williams@example.com"
}

### Update customer
PUT http://localhost:5014/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "John Updated",
  "surname": "Doe Updated",
  "email": "john.doe.updated@example.com"
}

### Delete customer
# DELETE http://localhost:5014/api/customers/3

